      <title>阿达尼、塔塔利润未达预期，印度股市前景堪忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/adani-tata-profit-misses-add-to-alarm-over-india-stocks-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[企业盈利进一步放缓引发了人们对印度 4.1 万亿美元股市的新一轮担忧，并有可能破坏印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪为恢复经济增长所做的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/adani-tata-profit-misses-add-to-alarm-over-india-stocks-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 04:17:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场等待中美谈判，小麦价格创三个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/wheat-reaches-three-month-high-as-market-awaits-us-china-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商考虑到中国对美国关税的谨慎态度，且市场等待世界两大经济体领导人可能举行的会谈细节，小麦价格触及近三个月来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/wheat-reaches-three-month-high-as-market-awaits-us-china-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 03:43:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
